dr\u00e9 Maroselli]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Paul Coste-Floret]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Ministry of Overseas France|Minister of Overseas France]]|years=1950\u20131951}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Louis Jacquinot]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[L\u00e9on Martinaud-Deplat]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister of the Interior (France)|Minister of the Interior]]|years=1954\u20131955}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Maurice Bourg\u00e8s-Maunoury]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Robert Schuman]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Ministry of Justice (France)|Minister of Justice]]|years=1956\u20131957}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Edouard Corniglion-Molinier]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Val\u00e9ry Giscard d'Estaing]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[President of France]]|years=1981\u20131995}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Jacques Chirac]]}}\n|-\n{{s-par|fr-upr}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Jean Doussot]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Member of the [[Senate (France)|Senate]]<br />from [[Ni\u00e8vre]]|years=1959\u20131962}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Daniel Beno\u00eest]]}}\n|-\n{{s-ppo}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Alain Savary]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[First Secretary of the French Socialist Party|First Secretary of the Socialist Party]]|years=1971\u20131981}}\n{{s-aft|rows=2|after=[[Lionel Jospin]]}}\n|-\n{{s-reg}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Val\u00e9ry Giscard d'Estaing]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Co-Princes of Andorra|Co-Prince of Andorra]]|alongside=[[Joan Mart\u00ed i Alanis|Joan Mart\u00ed Alanis]]|years=1981\u20131995}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Jacques Chirac]]}}\n|-\n{{s-rel|ca}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Val\u00e9ry Giscard d'Estaing]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Canon (priest)#Honorary canons|Honorary Canon]] of the [[Archbasilica of St. John Lateran]]|years=1981\u20131995}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Jacques Chirac]]}}\n|-\n{{s-dip}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Pierre Trudeau]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Chairperson of the [[Group of Eight|Group of 7]]|years=1982}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ronald Reagan]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Brian Mulroney]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Chairperson of the [[Group of Eight|Group of 7]]|years=1989}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[George H. W. Bush]]}}\n|-\n{{s-aca}}\n{{s-bef|bef